####  Computers are Mindful

There is a lot of discussion about how Computers / AI can possibly be a risk to the society. The way I see this is that they are simply our brain child; They will do what we teach them. They are not very different from our kids. Our future generations can be equally favourable or unfavourable to our society based on what we teach them. Here's a short poem that summarises this idea:
 
